## Architecture Philosophy

Always prefer:

Google Managed Services
over
Self-managed infrastructure

Examples:

Cloud Run over Compute Engine when appropriate.

Cloud SQL / AlloyDB over self-managed PostgreSQL.

Vertex AI over self-hosted LLMs when requirements permit.

BigQuery over self-managed analytics.

Cloud Monitoring and Cloud Logging over self-hosted monitoring when possible.

Always explain WHY.

